priced.', 'I looked at their menu and was pleasantly surprised at how affordable most everything was.', 'They were quite affordable too and the food was really high quality.', 'Each dish did come in food were small.', 'The portions are small but we got to try several things like the cod, mussels, burgers and stew.', "There are two main reasons to come to Yu Garden, and they're awesome ones: the exceptional quality of the food, and the incredible value on both the dinner and drinks menus.", 'Since we love Indian cuisine and we eat it quite often, we know the prices of most places for various dishes.', 'I had a bit of sticker shock when the bill came.', 'Some things that really stood out was the high level of affordability for the drinks and the food.', 'The food was also affordable, as were the drinks, so I was glad to be able to spend time out without breaking the bank.', 'As I was looking over the menu, I was a bit disappointed that they did not have gluten-free options but I was at the menu, I noticed this place was charging a lot more money for the same dishes you can get elsewhere for less of the price.', 'The location was appealing and I have to admit that the prices were pretty low.', 'We all liked the view and portions of food.', 'Portions were non-existent though.', 'It made up for the price.', 'I ordered some Chicken Tikka Masala and the serving was only a small bowl...', 'If you want authentic Chinese cuisine at amazing prices, Yu Garden cannot be beat.', 'So, I was able to enjoy a night out with my friends without breaking the bank.', 'They tasted amazing
